title: Episode 527 | "Between the Cheats"
description:
Joe and the guys give an update on the horrific shooting that took place in Brooklyn (21:40) and discuss the A$AP Rocky cheating on Rihanna rumors (41:10). Next, the crew debates if Drake's leaked verse was aimed at Pusha T (57:30), DaBaby's latest shootout (1:24:00), another installment of "Part of the Show" (1:47:25), and MORE!
